<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb8256c5c-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea" identifier="/us/usc/t5/s3707"><num value="3707">§ 3707.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Director of the Office of Personnel Management shall prescribe regulations for the administration of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb8256c5d-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/107/347/tII/s209/c/1">Pub. L. 107–347, title II, § 209(c)(1)</ref>, <date date="2002-12-17">Dec. 17, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/2930">116 Stat. 2930</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
